reviews.text: Very nice restaurant with variety of Italian options. Everything is well organized and well presented. The service is very good and professional. They have vegetarian menu. The timing and portions of serving are perfect. Would definitely recommend while being at Citygate outlet.

constantly good, attentive service. the pizzas are always freshly made and there are constantly new items being offered in their menus. if you don't mind dining at unusual hours, you can benefit from substantial discounts by using some discount apps. the service is always friendly and attentive with young staff doing their best to offer customers a pleasant experience. it's my favorite stop after a day in lantau and before heading back home.

Food is good, we have tried the dough balls, and a few different pizzas. The four cheese and garden pizza were pretty good. I prefer the classic doughbals with pesto rather than the dough balls with mushroom and cheese dip, it makes the appetiser too dense. service is fast but not that great. The staff doesn't give a warm and friendly vibe.
good food and service at affordable prices

reviews.text: 東涌人潮變多後，東薈城的食肆到處都要排隊，如果是去pizza express 我每次都是晚上1830提早去,不用等位就可以直接入店坐下了。我最喜歡的是他們的北京填鴨pizza, 真的是北京填鴨的醬和肉味，而且他們是用薄皮pizza, 配料和餅皮的比例做得相當好，不過我朋友覺得很重口味，點餐是點這款pizza, 餐廳就會捐錢給慈善機構。不過最近兩次去吃這款pizza，不知道是太繁忙還是換了師傅，那個薄餅皮焗得太燶了，而且這個餐廳沒有什麼套餐可選，小食種類也偏少。如果可以間中有居民優惠或者信用卡優惠，或者套餐的款式多一點，那就非常好了

Very nice restaurant with variety of Italian options. Everything is well organized and well presented. The service is very good and professional. They have vegetarian menu. The timing and portions of serving are perfect. Would definitely recommend while being at Citygate outlet.

自從呢區被攻佔後～都少左來～
今日係呢區收工見呢到好多位就入來食～
特別欣賞餐廳門面長～內裡燈光暗暗地工業風～
保守估計～侍應最少三分一應該都係講英文～

腌製品嘅小食拼盤正常出品～不過不失
醬汁雞翼唔太突出～
用北京填鴨做概念嘅烤鴨pizza～
醬汁味濃～偏鹹少少～
意式雲吞都應該係同普通超市出品差唔多～
餡料到味道都冇乜驚喜～
飲品方面點左奶昔～
飲品上面再加一層口口嘅忌廉～
入口滑溜～但偏都係偏甜

整體以連鎖式餐廳來計唔算太差～
發揮到應有水準但未至於一試難忘～

constantly good, attentive service. the pizzas are always freshly made and there are constantly new items being offered in their menus. if you don't mind dining at unusual hours, you can benefit from substantial discounts by using some discount apps. the service is always friendly and attentive with young staff doing their best to offer customers a pleasant experience. it's my favorite stop after a day in lantau and before heading back home.

Food is good, we have tried the dough balls, and a few different pizzas. The four cheese and garden pizza were pretty good. I prefer the classic doughbals with pesto rather than the dough balls with mushroom and cheese dip, it makes the appetiser too dense. service is fast but not that great. The staff doesn't give a warm and friendly vibe.
